# The service images build from the repository root because the service module
# `replace`s ../../sdk/go/*. Only those two module trees belong in the context;
# an allowlist keeps it that way as the repository grows, and in particular
# keeps the JavaScript workspace, the docs tree and any agent worktree checked
# out under .claude/ from being uploaded to the daemon on every build.
*
!sdk/go/
!services/agentnexus/

# Re-exclude what may appear inside an allowed tree.
**/node_modules/
**/*.exe
**/*.test
